<HL>
   Census Bureau
   Says It Missed
   2% of Population
   ----
   By Timothy Noah
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/19/91
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A9F
</SO>
<GV>
